#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:1
msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "入门"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:3
msgid ""
"For new users of Hi-net data, I highly recommend you request and download "
"waveform data from Hi-net website and try to process the data using "
"win32tools. Do all the things **manually** at least one time, make sure that "
"you understand the whole procedure and the limitations of Hi-net website."
msgstr ""
"对于Hi-net数据的新用户，强烈建议你至少一次手动从Hi-net申请并下载数据并尝试使"
"用 win32tools 处理数据，以确保你理解Hi-net数据申请、下载、处理的整个流程，并"
"了解Hi-net网站设计的不友好和诸多限制。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:8
msgid "Now let's get started."
msgstr "现在开始吧。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:10
msgid "Start python"
msgstr "启动Python"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:12
msgid ""
"Run `python` (or `ipython` if you have it), and make sure you're using "
"Python 3.10 or above:"
msgstr ""
"在终端中运行 `python` （或 `ipython` ），并确保你所使用的Python版本大于等于"
"3.10::"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:22
msgid "Create a Client"
msgstr "创建一个客户端"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:24
msgid ""
"HinetPy provides a {class}`~HinetPy.client.Client` class, which provides "
"several methods to help you get waveform data."
msgstr ""
"HinetPy 中的类 {class}`~HinetPy.client.Client` 提供了多个方法帮助你获取波形数"
"据。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:33
msgid "You need a Hi-net account to access Hi-net waveform data."
msgstr "你需要一个Hi-net账户以获取Hi-net台网的波形数据。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:36
msgid "Do checks"
msgstr "做一些检查"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:38
msgid ""
"Let {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.doctor` check if everything goes right:"
msgstr "用 {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.doctor` 检查是否一切正常："

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:48
msgid ""
"Congratulations! You're using the latest version of HinetPy, and the Hi-net "
"web service is NOT updated since the release of HinetPy, which means HinetPy "
"is still working. And you have `catwin32` and `win2sac_32` in your PATH. "
"Everything seems OK."
msgstr ""
"恭喜你！你正在使用HinetPy的最新版本，且Hi-net网站在这个版本HinetPy发布之后没"
"有再更新，这意味着HinetPy依然可以正常工作。并且，`catwin32` 和 `win2sac_32` "
"在你的PATH中。一切看起来都正常。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:53
msgid "Network Codes"
msgstr "台网代码"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:55
msgid ""
"Hi-net website provides seismic waveform data from several organizations and "
"networks, e.g. Hi-net, F-net and V-net. Each network has a unique network "
"code. In order to request waveform data from specified network, you need to "
"know the network code. See {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.info` for details."
msgstr ""
"Hi-net网站提供了来自于多个组织或台网的地震波形数据，比如Hi-net、F-net和V-"
"net。每个台网有唯一的台网代码。为了申请指定台网的波形数据，你必须首先知道台网"
"代码。使用 {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.info` 以了解更多信息。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:81
msgid ""
"Now we know Hi-net starts from 2004-04-01 and has a total number of 2336 "
"channels (about 780 stations)."
msgstr "现在我们知道Hi-net开始于2004-04-01，总共有2336个通道（约780个台站）。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:85
msgid ""
"Users are highly recommended to use [FnetPy](https://github.com/seisman/"
"FnetPy) if they need F-net data, since HinetPy cannot deal with F-net "
"instrumental responses correctly."
msgstr ""
"强烈建议Fnet用户使用 `FnetPy <https://github.com/seisman/FnetPy>`_ 获取Fnet数"
"据，因而HinetPy无法正确处理F-net的仪器响应。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:90
msgid "Stations"
msgstr "台站"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:92
msgid ""
"If you want, you can have a quick view of stations of Hi-net and F-net (Only "
"these two networks are supported). See {meth}"
"`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_station_list` for details."
msgstr ""
"你可以调用 {meth}`~HinetPy.client.Client.get_station_list` 以查看Hi-net和F-"
"net台网的台站信息（目前仅支持查看这两个台网的台站信息）。"

#: ../../tutorial/get-started.md:109
msgid ""
"Hi-net/F-net has a lot of stations. If you only need a few of them, you can "
"select the stations you want. Hi-net website also provides a web interface "
"to do that, which is preferred for most cases. If you want to dynamically "
"select stations in your script, you can try {meth}"
"`~HinetPy.client.Client.select_stations`."
msgstr ""
"Hi-net/F-net有很多台。如果你只需要申请其中某些台站的数据，你可以选择你需要的"
"台站。Hi-net网站提供了一个网页界面以筛选台站，通常建议值接使用这一网页界面。"
"如果你想要在申请的过程中动态选择台站，你可以使用 {meth}"
"`~HinetPy.client.Client.select_stations` 。"
